article:
One summer morning a tiger is walking near  a lake. He wants to eat something. He is very hungry. In the lake, a duck is swimming ."That is my breakfast," thinks the tiger.
"Good morning, Mr. Duck!" says the tiger.
"Go away, you bad tiger!" says the duck.
"I want to tell you something about your friend, Miss Chicken. If you don't come, I'll go. Good bye. Mr. Duck."
"Wait a minute," says the duck. "Tell me!"
The tiger looks around ,"I don't want other animals to know it. Come up to me," says the tiger. Then Mr. Duck swims to the tiger. As soon as(............) he gets to the bank ,the tiger gets it and eats it up.
He laughs best that laughs last..
